CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FA recovery truck driver accused of
OL,7,Fmurdering his 19-year-old girlfriend
OL,8,Fby pinning her against a lamppost with
OL,9,Fhis vehicle has told a jury he never
OL,10,Fwanted to hurt her.
OL,12,FProsecutors allege Lily Whitehouse
OL,13,Fsuffered catastrophic chest injuries
OL,14,Fwhen Mohammed Azim used his truck "as
OL,15,Fa weapon" to crush her during an
OL,16,Fargument in Oldbury on his 41st
OL,17,Fbirthday on November 5 2025.
OL,26,@vD@cOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FAzim, of Tividale Road in Tipton,
OL,7,Fdenied the murder of Ms Whitehouse,
OL,8,Fand told a jury at Wolverhampton Crown
OL,9,FCourt on Monday he accidentally hit Ms
OL,10,FWhitehouse after dropping her off near
OL,11,Fher home.
OL,13,FThe defendant wiped his eyes with a
OL,14,Ftissue in the witness box as he denied
OL,15,Fthe two, who had been in an on-off
OL,16,Frelationship since 2023, had been
OL,17,Farguing the night of the fatal
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FAzim allegedly picked Ms Whitehouse up
OL,7,Fafter she got off a bus from Russells
OL,8,FHall Hospital where she had been
OL,9,Fvisiting her baby in the neonatal
OL,10,Fintensive care unit, and was going to
OL,11,Fdrop her home in Amber Drive.
OL,13,FThe baby had been fathered by another
OL,14,Fman and born prematurely,
OL,16,FMs Whitehouse allegedly asked him to
OL,17,Fsit with her for 10 minutes before she
OL,18,Fwent home, so he pulled up in Old Park
OL,19,FLane nearby because it was a wider
OL,20,Froad for his van and the two chatted
OL,21,Fand scrolled on their phones.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FWhen asked by defence counsel Imran
OL,7,FShafi KC if they had been arguing,
OL,8,FAzim said: "No, no argument or
OL,9,Fnothing. She said she wanted to come
OL,10,Fwith me, she didn't want to go home.
OL,12,F"I was saying I need to go, it's been
OL,13,F10 minutes now I need to go home and
OL,14,Fhave an early night, I had to get up
OL,15,Fearly and go to work but she was
OL,16,Fpleading with me that she wanted to go
OL,17,Fwith me.
OL,19,F"She said I don't want go home, I want
OL,20,Fto spend more time."
OL,26,@pD@LOUtD@AOU{D@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FAzim said he got out of the van to hug
OL,7,Fher as she continued to ask to go back
OL,8,Fto his home.
OL,10,FHe said: "She come in the front (of
OL,11,Fthe van) and was stopping me, she was
OL,12,Fsaying no I'm not letting you go, I
OL,13,Fwant to go with you.
OL,15,F"I go back to the driver's side, open
OL,16,Fthe door and get in the truck and
OL,17,Fclose the door. She was trying to come
OL,18,Fin front of the truck.
OL,26,@rD@JOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,F"She's trying to stop me from the
OL,7,Ffront. I said please let me go. She
OL,8,Fwas trying to stop the van."
OL,10,FAzim said he started to drive slowly
OL,11,Fto the left to go around Ms Whitehouse
OL,12,Fbut had to swerve back to the right
OL,13,Fbecause of parked cars.
OL,15,FHe said: "I hear a bang at the back.
OL,16,FIt could have been Lily jumping on the
OL,17,Ftruck. I felt something bump the back.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@\O]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,F"I feel the back tyres, like something
OL,7,Fcome under the tyre or something drop
OL,8,Funder the tyre. I slammed the brake
OL,9,Fand straight away stopped.
OL,11,F"I looked back and saw Lily on the
OL,12,Ffloor in the middle of the road."
OL,14,FExplaining why he put Ms Whitehouse in
OL,15,Fhis van as he called 999, Azim said:
OL,16,F"I couldn't believe this was real.
OL,18,F"I was lost. I phoned the ambulance, I
OL,19,Fdidn't want to waste time and wait for
OL,20,Fan ambulance, I wanted to take her to
OL,21,Fthe hospital.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@aO]xD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,F"I didn't want to wait for nobody. I
OL,7,Fjust wanted to take her to the
OL,8,Fhospital, sometimes the ambulance is
OL,9,Ftoo long when you need them."
OL,11,FAzim said he pulled up in nearby Park
OL,12,FStreet while on the phone to 999
OL,13,Fbecause he "couldn't see the road
OL,14,Fstraight" and his head was "all over
OL,15,Fthe place".
OL,17,FHe said: "It was scary....I didn't
OL,18,Fthink she was breathing. I was still
OL,19,Fpraying and hoping she is unconscious
OL,20,Fand hoping the ambulance get there
OL,21,Fquick but it takes a long time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]uD@LOUvD@IO]vD@\OUwD@JO]yD@
OL,26,AJOU}D@`O]
