OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FAzim wiped his eyes with a tissue when
OL,7,FMr Shafi asked him how he felt that he
OL,8,Fhad killed Ms Whitehouse and why he
OL,9,Ftold the emergency services he had
OL,10,Fseen another car hit her.
OL,12,FHe said: "I didn't believe all this at
OL,13,Fthe time that it was me. I know I have
OL,14,Flied, it was a lie, but I don't know,
OL,15,FI couldn't believe this had happened.
OL,17,F"At that time, I don't know, I was
OL,18,Flost, my head was totally gone, I
OL,19,Fdon't know what I was thinking at the
OL,20,Ftime, I just couldn't believe it
OL,21,Fhappened with me."
OL,26,@tD@JOUyD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
