PN,34210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FHe added: "My head is hurting all this
OL,7,Ftime ... I wish this never happened."
OL,9,FAsked if he intended to hurt Ms
OL,10,FWhitehouse, Azim replied: "I never
OL,11,Fwanted to hurt Lily."
OL,13,FThe court heard Azim came to the UK in
OL,14,F2001 around the age of 14 and went to
OL,15,Fcollege and worked in takeaway
OL,16,Frestaurants to learn English.
OL,26,@nD@KOUoD@eO]rD@[OUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
