PN,34211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FThe defendant told the jury Ms
OL,7,FWhitehouse relied on him for support
OL,8,Fand that she did not have many
OL,9,Ffriends, so would text and call him
OL,10,Foften while he was working.
OL,12,FHe said: "When I was working she was
OL,13,Fmessaging me, if I can't reply to it
OL,14,For I'm doing something, I got a
OL,15,Frecovery truck and I do the cars and
OL,16,Fthat, sometimes I have gloves on my
OL,17,Fhands and can't message her.
OL,19,F"I could understand, she was lonely,
OL,20,Fshe got close to me and relying on me,
OL,21,Fshe didn't have any friends."
OL,26,@tD@JOU{D@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,FAzim denied ever assaulting Ms
OL,7,FWhitehouse and said she would text him
OL,8,Fasking if he was with another woman
OL,9,Ffor "attention".
OL,11,FHe said: "She send messages that are
OL,12,Fnot true to get my attention. I got to
OL,13,Fknow her background, I had a similar
OL,14,Fchildhood to her. I wanted to help her
OL,15,Fand be there for her.
OL,17,F"I never took anything serious because
OL,18,FI could understand where she was
OL,19,Fcoming from.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@OO]sD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
