OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781556458
OL,3,CDriver accused of murdering girlfriend
OL,4,Cwith truck says he hit her accidentally
OL,6,F"She would see me and say sorry to me,
OL,7,Fshe knew she was saying wrong on the
OL,8,Fphone just to see me.
OL,10,F"She never meant anything, it was
OL,11,Fnothing serious. I could understand
OL,12,Fwhy she was doing that, she never had
OL,13,Fno one else."
OL,15,FThe trial continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@MO]
